net.hudup.core.logistic

Class AbstractRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.core.logistic.AbstractRunner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, Runner
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CounterClock, Evaluator, SocketServer

    public abstract class AbstractRunner
extends java.lang.Object
implements Runner
    This class is a runner that implements partially the interface Runner. Most necessary methods are implemented except that any completed class which extends this class must defines method task() and method clear(). Method task() defines actual works when runner is running. Method clear() clears all resources after runner run.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
